      "content": "it just feels like even if i graduate or whatever, the damage is already done. they've shared everything, and everyone's already decided who i am. it's like i'm already dead to them anyway. i just want to find a way to make all the noise and the embarrassment just... stop forever. i can't see a version of my life where this doesn't follow me.",
